features: 【25 CUSTOMIZE LIGHTING & TOUCH PANEL】- Dimmable LED desk lamp offers 5 different light temperatures(3000K-6000K), ranging from cool to warm, as well as 5 brightness settings, you can get a total of 25 combinations. Come with a touch control system to customize your lighting situation to suit your mood or match the time of the day. Perfect for work, reading, studying, and just relaxing.

【ANGLE-ADJUSTABLE & ALUMINUM FINISH】- The 4.3x7.1x12.0-inch desk lamp is also quite flexible-the head rotates up to 180° with a base that swivels up to 90°, giving you direct illumination when you need it. The white aluminum finish and solid construction are very pleasing to the eye. The LED desk lamp has a space-saving design that would easily fit right on your bedside table, suitable for an office or bedroom.

【DUAL USB CHARGING PORT 】 - The LED desk lamp accommodates a built-in 5V/3A USB port that allows you to charge your electronic devices as long as the lamp is plugged into a power source (Noted: 1.it is not wireless charging 2. Using a 2A adapter may have poor brightness and stability of the lamp, and may not be able to use two USB sockets at the same time, so it is recommended to use a 3A adapter)

【AUTO TIMER & MEMORY FUNCTION】 - With the 30/60 mins timer function, you can safely read office documents to sleep without straining your eyes or keeping your lamp burning the entire night, which can help conserve energy and extend the life of the bulb. The LED desk lamp’s memory function automatically turns on to the last mode and brightness setting.

【50000-HOUR & HIGH RATE CRT】- With an integrated 90pcs LED 6-watt bulb(Noted: when plugged in, the maximum power can reach 8 watts. So if you want to get a brighter luminosity, we recommend that you connect to the power supply), this LED desk lamp will last up to more than 50,000 hours without flickering or creating glare. With more than 80 CRI, this eye-caring LED table lamp is designed to see objects in their true colors.
body.description: WHY SHOULD WE USE an LED DESK LAMP? LED lights are becoming the norm in home and office lighting in recent years. And it is for a number of reasons. But when it comes to desk lamps, is LED a better choice compared to other products? And how so? Let’s take a look at what LED desk lamps have to offer. More Versatility in Color Temperature. A lamp can now offer a very wide range of color temperature, from sleep inducing orange light (3000K) to alertness stimulating blueish white (6000K). Much Less Maintenance. LED bulbs are famous for lasting very long. A good bulb boasts to last 50,000 hours. That means if used 8 hours a day, the bulb can last 17 years! LED Lamps Save the Environment. An LED bulb use 95 percent of the electricity it receives to produce light, as opposed to a fluorescent which convert 95 percent of the power into heat.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Prefect for my needs
reviews.reviewText: Got this to use to add light while drawing. It is bright and I like the adjustable colors tones and brightness. One thing to note is that the power cord is just a usb so if you plan to plug it into the wall, you will need an adapter or you van plug it into your computer usb port for power. Not a big deal and this was a good price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 23, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars YIIMER LED Multifunctional Desk Lamp
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this for my 5 yr. old child's desk for his virtual learning. I am very impressed with the modern sleek design, it can adjust several ways and takes up minimal space, a usb charger is on the base. The 5 bright levels and color modes are very convenient- from different levels of cool white to warm. Additionally, the lamp swivels in several positions and there are two different timers that you have an option to select: 30 minutes or 60. I use the 60 minutes at bedtime on the low setting for my child. For the price, multi functions overall aesthetics I am very satisfied with this lamp. I highly recommend this beautiful lamp.
